[b]Munchausen HD[/b] - help the legendary baron Munchausen save the wonderful princes and all the kingdom. Help him in amazing adventures. The brave hero of this game for Android responded to the call for help of the princess. He travels through gloomy lands to save the princess from the evil wizard who has insidious plans to seize power in the kingdom. Help the hero find a lot of hidden items that you need to perform various tasks. Solve logic puzzles and play fun mini-games. Defeat the villain.

[b]Game features:[/b]

Great graphics
Beautiful locations
Interesting tasks
Difficult puzzles
Absorbing mini-games
